                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9944" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PJMT-0161</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1466 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智赋能 破茧成蝶：YH制造公司智能化改造项目成本管理的&quot;智&quot;变跃迁</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Empowering with digital intelligence to Emerge stronger from challenges: the &quot;smart&quot; transformation of cost management in YH Manufacturing Company&#39;s intelligent transformation project</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">田波，荆诗淇，陈佳宁，薛勇，刘昌辉，王拓，葛安康</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林省沅合轨道车辆配件有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">项目成本管理；智能化改造项目；多级挣值法；质量成本偏差分析法；数智化工具；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Intelligent Transformation Project；Project Cost Management；Multi Level Earned Value Method；Quality Cost Deviation Analysis Method；Digital Tools</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">振兴东北老工业基地政策的长期催化与新一轮制造业智能化改造国家战略的叠加驱动下，传统制造企业正面临从“经验主导”向“数据驱动”的转型挑战。传统项目成本管理模式因无法适应智能化改造项目特性而频繁失效。本案例聚焦YH公司Z车间智能化改造项目成本管理在各阶段暴露的具体问题及相应的优化措施，系统讲述了YH公司将挑战化为机遇，顺应智能化改造与数字化转型大背景重构项目成本管理新布局的过程。在此过程中，YH公司原有成本管理模式陷入了成本规划权责不清、流程粗放；成本估算依赖模板、缺乏实时数据；成本预算僵化、风险应对滞后；成本控制忽略层级关联与子项独立等困境。通过确立权责矩阵、重塑规划框架、研发数智比价系统、进行精细化估算、设置动态预算调节机制、升级ERP系统及利用多级挣值法与质量成本偏差分析协同控制成本，并对多级挣值法进行了创新改进等方式，YH公司最终实现了智能化改造项目成本管理的成功变革。本案例旨在引导学员深入理解数智时代下的项目成本管理新思路，有效提高其将数字化工具及创新方法应用于项目成本管理实践的能力，同时启发其对AI、大数据等数字化技术赋能项目成本管理的创新思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Under the long-term catalysis of policies revitalizing the old industrial base in Northeast China and the strategic drive of the new round of national initiatives for intelligent transformation of manufacturing, traditional manufacturing enterprises are facing challenges in transitioning from &#39;experience-driven&#39; to &#39;data-driven&#39;. Traditional project cost management models frequently fail due to their inability to adapt to the characteristics of intelligent transformation projects. This case study focuses on the specific issues exposed at each stage of the cost management of YH Company&#39;s Z workshop intelligent transformation project and corresponding optimization measures. It systematically narrates how YH Company turned challenges into opportunities, reconstructing a new cost management layout in line with the backdrop of intelligent transformation and digitalization. During this process, YH Company&#39;s original cost management model encountered difficulties such as unclear responsibilities in cost planning, crude processes; reliance on templates for cost estimation, lack of real-time data; rigid cost budgeting, delayed risk response; and neglect of hierarchical correlation and sub-item independence in cost control. By establishing a responsibility matrix, reshaping the planning framework, developing a digital intelligence comparison system, conducting detailed estimation, setting up dynamic budget adjustment mechanisms, upgrading the ERP system, and utilizing multi-level earned value analysis and quality cost deviation analysis for coordinated cost control, along with innovative improvements to the multi-level earned value method, YH Company ultimately achieved successful transformation in cost management for intelligent transformation projects. This case aims to guide learners to deeply understand new approaches to project cost management in the digital age, effectively enhancing their ability to apply digital tools and innovative methods to project cost management practices, while also inspiring them to think innovatively about how AI, big data, and other digital technologies can empower project cost management.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《项目管理》、《项目管理应用》、《项目成本管理》、《智能化改造项目》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">智能化改造项目定义与特点；项目成本管理；多级挣值法；质量成本偏差分析法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
